1.  kathe mi termatiki diergasia ftiaxnei kai apo mia swlinwsi. ta read/write 
    twn paidiwn einai asfalh (grafoume 4 bytes kathe fora, poly mikrotero 
    tou PIPE_BUF ~ 4096)

2.  oi diergasies boroun na trexoyn parallhla => h ekfrash apotimatai kata
    meri me pio grigoro tropo (efoson to overhead tis dimiourgias processes
    einai mikrotero)